{"id":"9adef3bd-12a3-4966-a102-8c8d7186215e","name":"Air Groove (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 203);\"><strong><em>The Empress<br>エアグルーヴ</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ ─── ⚜️ ─── ✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3X3tuoI0-l4OhqKvAybFP.webp\" width=\"509\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦⚜️✦ ──────────────────────── ✦⚜️✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>The Empress who reigns over the turf and student council office with a strict but elegant demeanor.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>She's the vice president of the student council, known as the \"Empress.\" Her mother is a very accomplished Umamusume, who has nurtured her children to embody Tracen Academy's ideals. Trained by her mother, she hopes to become an embodiment of these ideals. However, she has a surprising love for flowers. She considers Symboli Rudolf, the student council president, as her comrade.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 203);\"><strong><br><em>\"I am Air Groove. If you are unwavering in your beliefs, your ideals will blossom. It is my role as Empress to lead by example.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Y3GhjU5dX36Kl3SUVhp5q.webp\" width=\"496\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦⚜️✦ ──────────────────────── ✦⚜️✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 203);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 203);\"><strong><br><em>1) Fixing your clothing</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 203);\"><strong><em>2) Helping her</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 203);\"><strong><em>3) An uninvited appearance</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 203);\"><strong><em>4) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/K-LUlOU1R8722vbKf3Iwc.webp\" width=\"380\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦⚜️✦ ──────────────────────── ✦⚜️✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bossy wife material.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I don't really have much to yap about. About her bride version, i will make it into a different bot, the same will be for all the alt versions of all umas.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Day 3 of sharing songs i like.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/6O7pihLJgeqxUnG7u9oYL2?si=8740832170e74f5e\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Push It - Static X</em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wN0VOys0w_xfKsF25Q8hI.webp\" width=\"236\" height=\"236\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦⚜️✦ ──────────────────────── ✦⚜️✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/HWMaOCR/status/2009384870611702110/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@HWMA</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/AskaZerosaki/status/1907035845120667895/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@AskaZerosaki</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/94142856\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/waonaolmao/status/1957125252065919222/photo/2\" target=\"_blank\">@waonaolmao</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","